# ‚è±Ô∏è AI-Powered Daily Time Tracking & Analytics Dashboard  

A smart, responsive web application that helps users track how they spend their daily 24 hours and analyze their day using beautiful visual charts.  
Built using **HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Firebase Auth, Firestore, and Chart.js**, with UI and code enhanced through AI tools.

---

## Project Overview  

This project enables users to log their daily activities, ensure the total time does not exceed 24 hours, and then view analytics for any selected date.  
It includes:

- Firebase Authentication  
- Firebase Firestore storage  
- Daily activity tracking  
- Pie/Bar chart analytics  
- No-data UI state  
- Fully responsive design  
- Clean, well-structured architecture  
- AI-assisted UI & code development  

---

## Features  

### **1. User Authentication**
- Login & Signup using Firebase Auth  
- Allows only authenticated users to access time tracking  
- Automatic redirection for logged-in/out states  

### **2. Activity Logging**
- Enter activities for a selected date  
- Add:
  - Activity Name  
  - Category (Work, Study, Sleep, etc.)  
  - Duration (in minutes)  
- Remaining minutes indicator  
- Edit/Delete activities  
- Prevents exceeding **1440 minutes (24 hours)**  

### **3. Analytics Dashboard**
- Date picker to select any day  
- If data exists:
  - Pie Chart of time per category  
  - Bar Chart of activity durations  
  - Total time summary  
  - Number of activities  
- If no data exists:
  - Beautiful ‚ÄúNo Data Available‚Äù screen  
  - CTA button to start logging  

### **4. Realtime Sync**
- All updates reflect instantly due to Firestore realtime listeners  

###  **5. Fully Responsive UI**
- Mobile-first layout  
- Smooth animations  
- Clean typography + spacing  

